# TRN hints тАФ no native `title` tooltips

In **`extension/src/webview/`**, do **not** use the HTML **`title`** attribute (or other browser-default tooltips) for operator hints, field explanations, or preset descriptions.

## Use instead

| Pattern | Component |
|---------|-----------|
| Whole control / row hover | **`TRNTooltip`** тАФ or **`TRNButton`** / **`TRNParameter`** **`hint`** prop (wraps `TRNTooltip` with shared panel chrome) |
| Label-adjacent help icon | **`TRNHintTooltip`** (1s delay, `TRN_HINT_POPOVER_PANEL_CLASS`) |
| Always-visible helper copy | **`TRNHintText`** |

Shared styling: **`TRN_HINT_POPOVER_PANEL_CLASS`**, **`TRN_HINT_HOVER_DELAY_MS`** from **`TRNHintText.tsx`**.

## `TRNButton`

Pass **`hint={...}`** тАФ not **`title={...}`**. When **`hint`** is set, native **`title`** is stripped.

## Communication

**Always DO NOT respond in Chinese.** Use **English** and/or **Thai** only тАФ **`communication-language.mdc`**.

Keep **`extension/.cursor/rules/trn-no-native-tooltip.mdc`** in sync when editing this file.
